query:
SELECT
                    AVG(b.build_finished - b.build_started) AS "duration!: Duration"

                FROM
                    crates AS c
                    INNER JOIN releases AS r on c.id = r.crate_id
                    INNER JOIN builds AS b on r.id = b.rid

                WHERE
                    c.id = $1 AND
                    b.build_status = 'success' AND
                    b.build_started IS NOT NULL
